### ============================================================
### 친구 시스템 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 친구 목록 조회 (페이징)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 전체 친구 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 친구 수 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/count
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 친구 요청 보내기
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/request
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "friendId": "target-user-id",
  "message": "Let's be friends!"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 받은 친구 요청 목록
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/requests/received
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 보낸 친구 요청 목록
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/requests/sent
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 친구 요청 수락
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/requests/1/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 친구 요청 거절
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/requests/1/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 친구 요청 취소
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/requests/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 친구 삭제
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/friend-user-id
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 사용자 차단
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/block/target-user-id
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 차단 해제
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/block/target-user-id
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 차단 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/blocked
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 친구 여부 확인
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/check/target-user-id
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
